程序包的使用
net.opentsdb.query.expression

  • 使用net.opentsdb.query.expression的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    net.opentsdb.query.expression  
    net.opentsdb.query.expression.parser  
    net.opentsdb.query.pojo  
  • net.opentsdb.query.expression使用的net.opentsdb.query.expression中的类 
    类和说明
    Expression
    The interface for various expressions/functions used when querying OpenTSDB.
    ExpressionDataPoint
    Contains the information for a series that has been processed through an expression iterator.
    ExpressionIterator
    A iterator that applies an expression to the results of multiple sub queries.
    ExpressionTree
    A node in a tree of nested expressions.
    ITimeSyncedIterator
    An interface for expressions or queries that operate across time series and require point-by-point timestamp synchronization.
    NumericFillPolicy
    POJO for serdes of fill policies.
    NumericFillPolicy.Builder
    A builder class for deserialization via Jackson
    VariableIterator
    An interface that helps merge different time series sets (e.g. different metrics with a group by operator).
    VariableIterator.SetOperator
    An operator that determines how to sets of time series are merged via expression.
